Developer Terms of Use
des:
Lunch Menu lets users know what is being served in the cafeteria per the official lunch calendar released by the school.

Users can find out what is for lunch on the day of the request as well as the following day.

Lunch Menu is currently available for these schools:
South Lebanon Elementary School - Maineville, OH

Should you wish to feature your school's menu on "Lunch Menu" - reach out to us at lunchmenuskill@gmail.com.
